name: Craft a Logo by Hand
seo_title: Designing Course - Learn How to Create a Hand Drawn Logo
seo_description: Learn how to create a hand drawn logo with this practical and highly-actionable online design course and boost your logo design skills
description: Create a hand-drawn logo by turning your hand lettering into professional vector artwork. This course covers relevant history, terminology & practical tips to help you improve your skills & gain an appreciation for hand lettering in brand design.
